# This plugin ships SELF-CONTAINED (see SELF-CONTAINED-BUILD-PLAN.md): dist/ holds
# committed, dependency-inlined esbuild bundles so a fresh marketplace install runs
# with ZERO runtime `npm install`. dist/ is therefore INTENTIONALLY TRACKED — do not
# add it here. The CI freshness gate rebuilds it and fails on drift.
#
# node_modules/ is a maintainer-only dev install (build + tests) and stays ignored.
node_modules/

# Never ignore the committed bundles, even if an ancestor .gitignore later adds dist/.
!dist/
!dist/**

# The tray app (TRAY-APP-PLAN.md) ships fully self-contained: the systray2 Go
# helper binaries and the rasterized sunflower icons are COMMITTED so the tray
# runs on a fresh clone with zero `npm install`. Explicit allow-rules keep them
# tracked despite any broad ancestor ignore.
!bin/
!bin/**
!assets/app-icon*
